    "This approach maximises the number of objects with high-S/N GAAP flux measurements in all bands, and yields the best possible photo-z from the combined KiDS+VIKING data.To demonstrate the quality of the ten-band photometric catalogues and the cross-survey calibration, in Fig. 24 we present an optical and NIR colour-colour diagram for KiDS DR5 sources.",
